Hippocho Augustin, zaka volkotat Sant Augustine vo Sant Austin muntlear, zaun aslo ek zanar, zachim boroupam Kristanv dormank ekdom upoegak poddlin bodolpak chintnam akea udentichea sonvsarant.

Zolom : 13ver Novembrache, 354 vorsa, Tagaste muntat tea Algeriachea dessant.
Morn : 28 August, 430 vorsa, Hippo Regius, Algeriachea dessant.

Akkem Nanv : Aurelius Augustinus Hipponensis
Ganv  : Algeria
Pai ani Maim : Monica, jivui Sant zali, ani Patricius Aurelius

Augustine zolmolo eka gavant zachem nanv Thagaste eka Afrika dessant, zachi razvodki choloitalo Rome ( atam Souk Ahras, Algeria). Tache mainchem nanv zaun aslem Monica, ek devbokti Kristanv Ani paichem nanv Patricius zo zaun aslo onbavarti, zo mornachea vellar Kristanv zallo.

Ekra vorsanche piraer paullo tednam taka iskolant gallo Madaurus muntat tea ganvant ( atam M'Daourouch), vo ganv Thagaste san 19 mil pois also. Hea iskolan to Latin shinklo, toxench onbavarteanche dek to shinkpak laglo.

17 vorsanche pirayer, Romanianus eka ganvkaran, Augustinak, fudlem shinkop korunk adar dilo, Taka Carthage munta tea ganvant daddlo. Zorui Augustin Kristanv dorman vaddlolo, to Kristanv dorm soddun Manichaea muntat tea dorman bitor sorlo, zaka lagon tachi maim, Monica, ekdom sintir zali. Burgea ponnar, Augustin ekdom mosteponnan jietalo tachea amigam sangta,je ekdom gorvan sangtalo kitlea bailam ani dadlea sangata tannim mojjean dis sarlet te. Te burge zaitea burgeank tosle sonvoink laitalet nam zalear fotti marun tankam tanchea zommean bitor sorpak meutalem. Hea vellar tannem aplem ek famad rozar kelem, munnon, Deva, mojem nirmolponn sambalpak tuzo maka adar dhi, punn atanch nui.

19 vorsanche pirayer Augustinachi amizad zali eke ostorechi, teach Carthage ganvant. Goddiek zait tannem ti amizad keli fokot aple mayk lagon ji taka kazar korun soddtali tanchea zatachea cheddva lagim. 13 vorsam passun Augustanin te ostorecho mogan ravlo. Tankam zolmolo ek cholo zachem nanv Adeodatus zo ekdom huxear aslo. 385 vorsa Augustinan te ostorek sodli, eke guirest ostore lagim kazar zaupak.

